<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MAKXIM Links</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
    }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(32, 24, 21, .72), rgba(32, 24, 21, .86)),
        url("data:image/jpeg;base64,") center/cover fixed;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px 14px 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 430px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 98px;
      height: 98px;
      margin: 8px auto 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: url("data:image/jpeg;base64,") center/cover;
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.05;
      font-weight: 850;
      letter-spacing: .5px;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
    }

    .bio {
      margin: 10px auto 18px;
      max-width: 365px;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.38;
      font-weight: 650;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.94);
      text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
    }

    .notice {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      padding: 15px 16px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 198, 86, .18);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 198, 86, .72);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.26);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .notice-title {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #ffe0a0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .notice-text {
      margin: 0;
      color: #fff7e9;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-weight: 650;
    }

    .link {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 68px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      margin: 13px 0;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #17110f;
      background: rgba(207, 183, 171, .90);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: transform .14s ease, filter .14s ease;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .link:active {
      transform: scale(.985);
    }

    .icon {
      position: absolute;
      left: 18px;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #111;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    }

    .icon img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .creator {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 13px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(18,18,20,.54);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.93);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      font-weight: 750;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.62);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 650;
    }

    @media (max-width: 380px) {
      body { padding-left: 12px; padding-right: 12px; }
      h1 { font-size: 31px; }
      .bio { font-size: 16px; }
      .link { font-size: 16px; min-height: 64px; }
      .icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; left: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="avatar"></div>

    <h1>MAKXIM</h1>

    <div class="bio">
      🎮 Fortnite Clips, 1v1s & Highlights<br>
      💙 Creator Code: MAKXIM
    </div>

    <section class="notice">
      <span class="notice-title">⚠️ Wichtig für TikTok-Nutzer</span>
      <p class="notice-text">
        Falls nach dem Klick auf einen Link eine TikTok-Meldung erscheint:
        oben rechts auf <b>⋮</b> tippen und <b>„Im Browser öffnen“</b> auswählen.
      </p>
    </section>

    <a class="link" href="https://discord.gg/xMd8wmfQRa">
      <span class="icon"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Discord"></span>
      💬 Discord beitreten
    </a>

    <a class="link" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@makximfn">
      <span class="icon"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="TikTok"></span>
      🎵 TikTok
    </a>

    <a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/makximfn">
      <span class="icon"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Instagram"></span>
      📸 Instagram
    </a>

    <div class="creator">
      💙 Supporte mich mit Creator Code: <b>MAKXIM</b>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      MAKXIM Community
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
